---
const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href={`${baseUrl}icon.png`} />
  <title>Privacy Policy — Zoom-In Chile</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@700&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    :root {
      --bg: #0F1D24;
      --bg-card: #162A35;
      --accent: #E25822;
      --text: #EAEAEA;
      --text-dim: #8A9BA5;
      --font-display: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      --font-body: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
    }
    body {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
    }
    nav {
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }
    nav a {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    nav a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    nav img { height: 28px; border-radius: 6px; }
    h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .updated {
      color: var(--text-dim);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--accent);
    }
    p, li {
      color: var(--text-dim);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
    a { color: var(--accent); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <a href={baseUrl}>
      <img src={`${baseUrl}icon.png`} alt="" />
      <span>&larr; Zoom-In Chile</span>
    </a>
  </nav>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: April 8, 2026</p>

    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>Zoom-In Chile ("the App") is developed by Depointless. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting any data related to your use of the App.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>The App collects minimal data:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Game progress:</strong> Stored locally on your device using SharedPreferences. This data does not leave your device.</li>
      <li><strong>Leaderboard entries:</strong> If you submit a score, your initials (3 characters) and score are sent to our server. No personally identifiable information is collected.</li>
      <li><strong>Advertising:</strong> The App uses Google AdMob, which may collect device identifiers and usage data for ad personalization. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>Game progress is stored locally on your device. Leaderboard data is stored on our secure server. We do not sell, share, or transfer your data to third parties beyond what is described above.</p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>The App is rated for Everyone. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Google AdMob (advertising)</li>
      <li>Google Play Services</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@depointless.cl">contact@depointless.cl</a>.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
